  <h2>How this becomes public practice</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    <article class="card"><span class="status status-implemented">small group</span><h3>Term check</h3><p>Before conflict escalates, list the load-bearing words and ask each person what they mean by them.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><span class="status status-implemented">institution</span><h3>Definition ledger</h3><p>Publish operative definitions, revision history, dispute process, and examples of borderline cases.</p></article>
    <article class="card"><span class="status status-implemented">self-governance</span><h3>Meaning hygiene</h3><p>When confused, stop arguing the conclusion and define the terms. Most false conflicts hide there first.</p></article>
